OL,3,CKemi Badenoch urges Conservative
OL,4,Ccouncils to challenge asylum hotels
OL,6,FIn a letter to Tory councils, Badenoch
OL,7,Fsaid she was "encouraging" other local
OL,8,Fauthorities to "take the same steps"
OL,9,Fas Epping Council, "if your legal
OL,10,Fadvice supports it."
OL,12,FLabour dismissed her letter as
OL,13,F"desperate and hypocritical nonsense,"
OL,14,Fbut several of its own local councils
OL,15,Fhave already suggested they could
OL,16,Fmount legal action of their own
OL,17,Fagainst asylum hotels in their areas.
