OL,3,CKemi Badenoch urges Conservative
OL,4,Ccouncils to challenge asylum hotels
OL,6,FIn her letter, Badenoch praised Epping
OL,7,FCouncil's legal challenge and told
OL,8,FTory councils she would "back you to
OL,9,Ftake similar action to protect your
OL,10,Fcommunity."
OL,12,FWhile she added that the situation
OL,13,Fwould "depend on individual
OL,14,Fcircumstances of the case," she went
OL,15,Fon to suggest Tory councils could
OL,16,Fpursue "other planning enforcement
OL,17,Foptions."
