OL,3,CKemi Badenoch urges Conservative
OL,4,Ccouncils to challenge asylum hotels
OL,6,FShe also accused Labour of "trying to
OL,7,Fram through such asylum hotels without
OL,8,Fconsultation and proper process,"
OL,9,Fsaying the government had reopened the
OL,10,FBell Hotel as asylum accommodation
OL,11,Fafter the Conservatives had closed it.
OL,13,FThe hotel had previously been used as
OL,14,Fasylum accommodation briefly in 2020
OL,15,Fand then between 2022 and 2024 under
OL,16,Fthe previous Conservative government.
