OL,3,CKemi Badenoch urges Conservative
OL,4,Ccouncils to challenge asylum hotels
OL,6,FEpping secured a temporary injunction
OL,7,Ffrom the High Court on Tuesday,
OL,8,Fblocking the use of the Essex town's
OL,9,FBell Hotel as accommodation for asylum
OL,10,Fseekers on planning grounds.
OL,12,FThe decision has prompted councils
OL,13,Fcontrolled by Labour, the
OL,14,FConservatives and Reform UK to
OL,15,Finvestigate whether they could pursue
OL,16,Fa similar course of action.
