OL,3,CKemi Badenoch urges Conservative
OL,4,Ccouncils to challenge asylum hotels
OL,6,FThese include Labour-run Tamworth and
OL,7,FWirral councils, Tory-run Broxbourne
OL,8,Fand East Lindsey councils and Reform's
OL,9,FStaffordshire and West
OL,10,FNorthamptonshire councils.
OL,12,FBut Labour's Newcastle City Council
OL,13,Fand Brighton and Hove City Council
OL,14,Fhave both ruled out legal action.
OL,16,FTuesday's High Court decision has also
OL,17,Fcaused difficulty for the Home Office,
OL,18,Fwhich has a legal duty to house
OL,19,Fdestitute asylum seekers while their
OL,20,Fclaims are being dealt with.
