OL,3,CKemi Badenoch urges Conservative
OL,4,Ccouncils to challenge asylum hotels
OL,6,FIf planning laws prevent the
OL,7,Fgovernment from using hotels,
OL,8,Fministers will face a scramble to find
OL,9,Falternative accommodation, potentially
OL,10,Fin the private rented sector.
OL,12,FA Labour spokesperson said Mrs
OL,13,FBadenoch's letter was a "pathetic
OL,14,Fstunt" and "desperate and hypocritical
OL,15,Fnonsense from the architects of the
OL,16,Fbroken asylum system," saying there
OL,17,Fwere now "20,000 fewer asylum seekers
OL,18,Fin hotels than at their peak under the
OL,19,FTories."
