OL,6,FThe letter comes ahead of the
OL,7,Fpublication on Thursday of figures
OL,8,Fshowing how many asylum seekers were
OL,9,Fbeing temporarily housed in hotels at
OL,10,Fthe end of June this year.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FHome Office figures from the previous
OL,18,Fquarter show there were 32,345 asylum
OL,19,Fseekers being housed temporarily in UK
OL,20,Fhotels at the end of March.
